  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA70">
<l>aṭarppoṉ muṭiyāṉai yāyirampē rāṉai</l>
<l>cuṭarkoḷ cuṭarāḻi yāṉai yiṭarkaṭiyu</l>
<l>mātā pituvāka vaittē ṉeṉatuḷḷē</l>
<l>yātākil yātē yiṉi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one with a crown of thick gold, the one with the thousand names,</l>
<l>the one with the glow-absorbing glowing discus – I who have adopted</l>
<l>him as mother and father who chase away affliction, for my mind,</l>
<l>if there be what, what now?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
